{
  "stem": "27351.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Somehow, he-- maybe he thought that we may be in Czestochowa rather than in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was then 18 [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] or 17.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he walked all the way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And this is far away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This is from the northeastern part of the-- of Poland to the southwestern part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He avoided big cities.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And was walking through villages, stopping there to do some work, being fed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Of course, you know, he never disclosed his Jewish origin.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And finally, he came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He came to Czestochowa sometimes in October, or maybe it was November, 1941.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So the two of us were together, and pretty soon my mother joined us, too.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "She also escaped the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And, again, either I don't remember, or I didn't ask her, I don't know the details of-- of her escape.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I would--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was a good feeling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But unfortunately, I don't remember very much, or I never asked him any details of his life with my father, his life in-- in the Russian part of Poland.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember only a few Russian songs that she-- or that he was singing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These were the first Russian songs I heard, and I liked them very much.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't think I will.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my mother came.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were the three of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Again, there was no money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We lived in the kitchen of-- of my youngest uncle's apartment.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a room and a very small, narrow kitchen.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this is where we settled.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This young man, we called him [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Romek. ?] His Jewish name was [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Reuven, ?] was-- had a-- was a tailor also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he had a wife with some type of congenital heart disease, And At that time, she was bedridden.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She just couldn't walk.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
